attachments.title: GDG Devfest Liverpool - CFP
attachments.text: We are very excited to announce that the call for speakers for GDG Devfest Liverpool is now open! The event will take place on November 25th at the Hilton Liverpool City Centre Hotel (3 Thomas Steers Way, Liverpool L1 8LW).The day will be split into two tracks, one technology focussed, one design/creativity focussed. We are looking for people to come share some of the best insights they have into any of the following:Tech track:- Android- Web / Chrome- Firebase - Google Cloud Platform- Any other Google Technology- Any other technology topic you think is worthwhile sharingCreative track:- Material Design- Motion in Design- Any other design topic you think is worthwhile sharingWhen submitting, please follow the criteria that matches the style of your session.Session criteria:#Talk - 45 min presentation (inclusive of Q&A)#Workshop - 45 minutes with hands on, practical, live demonstrations (inclusive of Q&A)#Lightning talk - 10-15 minute presentationWe can't wait to see what amazing topics people want to share, and look forward to seeing you all at Devfest Liverpool 2016!
